0:{"rsc":["$","$1","c",{"children":[["$","div",null,{"className":"min-h-screen flex flex-col","children":[["$","header",null,{"className":"px-6 lg:px-24 py-5 flex items-center justify-between bg-black text-background","children":["$","$L2",null,{"href":"/","children":["$","h3",null,{"className":"font-gloock text-3xl","children":"Freaks"}]}]}],["$","main",null,{"className":"flex-1 flex flex-col items-center justify-center px-6","children":["$","article",null,{"className":"w-full max-w-2xl lg:max-w-3xl font-eb-garamond text-lg lg:text-xl leading-relaxed space-y-6 py-16 font-libre-baskerville","children":[["$","h2",null,{"className":"text-3xl lg:text-5xl font-semibold","children":"Our Story"}],["$","section",null,{"className":"space-y-3","children":[["$","p",null,{"children":"Say the word consistency and it sounds like routine, repetition, and nothing worth talking about."}],["$","p",null,{"children":"But when you look at anyone who is actually great at what they do, the guitarists with calloused fingers, the coders who see logic in their sleep, the runners who hit the pavement in the pouring rain, you realize they aren't just “consistent.” They're obsessed. They're all in."}]]}],["$","section",null,{"className":"space-y-3","children":[["$","h3",null,{"children":"Potential Demands Action"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"We're all told we have “unlimited potential.” It's a nice sentiment, but potential doesn't actually mean anything if it's just sitting there."}],["$","p",null,{"children":"The only way to actually cash in on that potential is through the quiet, often invisible work of practice. Not the glamorous, montage-worthy practice, but the “I really don't want to do this today” kind of practice."}]]}],["$","section",null,{"className":"space-y-3","children":[["$","h3",null,{"children":"Where Consistency Wins"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"We believe that greatness isn't a lightning bolt. It's a scoreboard."}],["$","p",null,{"children":"That's why we focus on the consistency score. It's not about being a perfect human being 100% of the time (good luck with that). It's about owning your data. It's about seeing the “freak” in yourself.                    "}],["$","p",null,{"children":"We wanted to create a space for the people who care about the rhythm of their week. For the people who know that doing something small every single day is infinitely more powerful than doing something huge once a month."}]]}],["$","section",null,{"className":"space-y-3","children":[["$","h3",null,{"children":"The Freaks"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"We're here for the people who are a little too intense about their morning routine. For the ones who track their habits not because they have to, but because they love to show up, every single time. We want to know that when the world got messy, we stayed consistent."}],["$","p",null,{"children":"If you're the type of person who actually enjoys seeing your consistency climb from 70% to 80%, you're in the right place. You aren't “optimizing your life.”                You're shaping the pattern."}],["$","p",null,{"children":"And it adds up. Until one day, it's not effort anymore. It's just you."}]]}]]}]}],["$","footer",null,{"className":"px-6 lg:px-24 py-5 border-t flex flex-row items-center justify-between","children":[["$","$L2",null,{"href":"/","children":["$","h3",null,{"className":"font-gloock text-3xl","children":"Freaks"}]}],["$","div",null,{"className":"flex flex-row items-center gap-5","children":[["$","$L2",null,{"className":"hover-click","href":"/about","children":"About"}],["$","$L2",null,{"className":"hover-click","href":"/privacy","children":"Privacy Policy"}],["$","$L2",null,{"className":"hover-click","href":"/terms","children":"Terms & Conditions"}]]}]]}]]}],[["$","script","script-0",{"src":"/_next/static/chunks/0ka051yepewro.js","async":true}]],["$","$L3",null,{"children":["$","$4",null,{"name":"Next.MetadataOutlet","children":"$@5"}]}]]}],"isPartial":false,"staleTime":300,"varyParams":null,"